I"Ò<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>ssh <span class="nt">-o</span> <span class="s2">"UserKnownHostsFile=/dev/null"</span> <span class="nt">-o</span> <span class="s2">"StrictHostKeyChecking=no"</span> &lt;<span class="nv">$SSH_USER</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>@&lt;<span class="nv">$SSH_HOST</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
